{"tid":1608781,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"無搶槍，警察都係開槍","createTime":"2019-10-01T11:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T12:04:30.000Z","uid":280192,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fff6dfc548efeb30c92f962295e75624e7f59918","tid":1608781,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:50:35.000Z","msg":"宜家香港人無搶槍，警察都一樣會主動衝入來人堆，先起腳等你還拖就開槍。<br />\n<br />\n而咁啱發夢見到：<br />\n烏克蘭圍落單警察搶槍，失槍夠多，政府就宣布無法管治，全面跪低了。<br />\n<br />\n但係香港人，千奇唔好學烏克蘭人犯法呀，我地要守住光環，和平非理性非暴力，以德報怨，愛仇敵，做甘地，贏諾貝爾和平獎呀！"},{"pid":"d743e3623ab4ab9ce9fb0e646d5e977f1a641fe8","tid":1608781,"uid":248588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92b8645fb1eb6867b8ada94922e61338bcda140","tid":1608781,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e637da373131d18d1157ea92c46cdfb37293d7f","tid":1608781,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"做得到先算啦香港人"},{"pid":"2e0804f7e786d43f09a46fdd1e164dbfa975855e","tid":1608781,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3d35159eeec3cc50208a3500a77521bae1467c","tid":1608781,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:56:47.000Z","msg":"根本先前割席果班都係鬼。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfb760c5a9f4f19adddadc22db86a4aa54840fc","tid":1608781,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:58:28.000Z","msg":"1枝槍 = 6條命"},{"pid":"27285bb8071d8a088dd979075c6c2dfdf4773c15","tid":1608781,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0